Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miso-flavored pork bone stock\Nwith roast pork...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The two thick slices of\Nroast pork are on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I've been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.\NOur ramen noodles stay hot till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just not easy eating\Nwith my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this kind of makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like you and I are\N{\i1}getting closer to Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, lend me those chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Don't tell me, Sakura...\N{\i1}You're going to feed me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say ahh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the part for you\Nto butt in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "What"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when Sakura was\Nabout to feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When a friend is in trouble,\Nyou must help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a true friend does\Naccording to this book...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind reading books like that.\NJust read the situation, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I read something\Nthat I cannot see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto can't eat with\Nhis right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're having a little disagreement\Nover who's going to feed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So in the end, it's Kakashi Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kakashi Sensei, I'm surprised that you\N aren't in the hospital after a huge mission like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that how people\Nperceive me nowadays...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this time, I didn't need to use\Nmy Mangekyo Sharingan, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you all hadn't arrived in time,\NI would have used it again for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry... we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, just as you imagined,\NI'd probably be lying in bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...\NYou have definitely gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're equal to me,\Nor even stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But keep in mind that the greater the\N Jutsu you use, the greater the risk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi... This new Jutsu...\N{\i1}the Wind Style: Rasen-Shuriken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forbid Naruto from using it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he continues using this new Jutsu,\N {\i1}Naruto will lose his ability {\i1}to mold Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the cells are disconnected {\i1}from the body's Chakra Network,\N {\i1}even my medical skills won't cure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be certain to emphasize\N{\i1}that to Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That new Jutsu of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know myself best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be the Hokage one day,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really powerful,\Nso there's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have bothered\Nworrying about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess these should be the members\Nof the search team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Kakashi here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been notified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be having a hard time\Nwith Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kakashi will be able\Nto talk him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better put a guard on him\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sure to start training\Non that new Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he does that, he'll never be\N able to build up his Chakra again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If that happens, his career\Nas a Shinobi will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can't ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you investigating\Nthe Akatsuki Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped by because\NI was a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the details on what\Nyou said just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ramen, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Kakashi Sensei the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you've finally learned\Nto do the Shadow Clone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...let me see how much\Nyou've improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here I come, Big Bro Naruto.\N- Here I come, Big Bro Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sexy Two-girl Jutsu!\N- Sexy Two-girl Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...!\NSo that's your new move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, big brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The two girls are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Konohamaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Moegi, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in\Nfront of us ladies...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is like déjà vu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what you always do\Nwhen you get together, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, this Jutsu makes\Na good diversionary tactic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you could say this is a serious\N competition between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You two shouldn't be\Nescalating things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are the only ones who\Nwould fall for a Jutsu like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys seem to be having fun, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's the Pervy Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's another one\Nthat would fall for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You're looking better\Nthan I expected, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! The bones haven't healed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all.
Comment: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunade told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've perfected\Nthe Wind Style: Rasen-Shuriken...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have accomplished a feat not\N even the Fourth Hokage was able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Have more confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is the result,\Nthen it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mastered an Instant Kill Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but... it's pointless if I'm only going to\N waste my Chakra on top of getting injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a Jutsu that can\Nbe used over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to learn a couple Jutsu that\N use less Chakra, but are effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you were\Nworrying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, all you have to do\Nis train some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At your current level, there are sure\N to be other Jutsu that you can master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come with me on another journey\Nto gather writing material?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you if you have the will\Nto train with me once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Then we'll leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we must heal that arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we visit a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "hot spring"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see exactly where your thoughts\Nare headed, you Pervy Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I found a spa with mixed bathing\N that's good for healing broken bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that {\i1}is{\i0} your motive, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well that's too bad.\NMaybe I'll invite Sakura, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I'll go.\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm injured, you know...\NDon't leave me behind, Pervy Sage!
Comment: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally here!\NPervy Sage, let's start training!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?\N First, we wash off the dirt from our travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing your arm is also\Npart of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The hot spring here is\Ngood for broken bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot springs...are so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's research... Research!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, Pervy Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you nearly killed by Grandma Tsunade\N for peeking into the women's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I came,\NI'm sure it was a mixed bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they separated the bath\Nbecause of guys like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Just what have you\Nbeen learning from your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I do these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz you're a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The research for\Nthe Make-Out series is a cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is actually Ninja training to make oneself\N go unnoticed by women who are on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem... anyway, being here at these hot\N springs is really to treat your broken bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of soaking in the bath\Nas part of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervy Sage, hurry and train me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... You're such an annoying kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry about this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've trained so that instead of...\Nrelying on Nine-Tail's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than use a power\Nthat hurts everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've trained to attain the power to protect,\N but it's just not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervy Sage, isn't there\Na long-distance type Jutsu that I can learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking as though\Nhe's a full-fledged Ninja...
Comment: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervy Sage, do you think I've gotten\Na bit stronger at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same novice\Nyou were three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's what being wise means,\N {\i1}then I don't care if I'm a fool {\i1}for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even without a teacher, {\i1}I'll create some awesome\N Jutsu {\i1}and rescue Sasuke, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...have your feelings changed\Nsince three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I never take back my word.\NThat's my Ninja Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was concerned about my friend, {\i1}and what I gained\N from it was {\i1}a sense of helplessness and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet Naruto has lived {\i1}with the same\N regret for three years {\i1}without giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}on his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has never forgotten Sasuke\N{\i1}and has continued to train...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Earnest in his desire to bring\N{\i1}Sasuke back home to Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if his own body is battered...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The idiot has matured in his idiot way.\NI'll acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But in order to bring him back,\NI've gotta get much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe he can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, "a place where someone still thinks\N of you, that's a place you can call home."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there...\NThere's a dango shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been walking all day.\NI'm exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look exhausted at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so easygoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But Senpai, we're trying to\Ncatch a Tailed Beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,yet we don't even know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nwhat are we going to catch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-Tails! Three-Tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One-Tail, Two-Tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Tobi! Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's dango for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It looks yummy!\NLet's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's so good!\NThis sauce is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too sweet, nor too salty.\NIt's a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai, Senpai. Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks exactly like your work, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that your work is...\Na rip-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you!
Comment: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we all have to\Nacknowledge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gamatatsu, Gamakichi,\NSakura, Tsunade...and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We all admit you've worked\Nreally hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's pushing you forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I never give up and I have guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sasuke will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,acknowledge that about me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell him about the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to do,\Nso I must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go back to the village and \Nhelp with the rest of Naruto's training?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it if you give me\Nsome snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.\NI'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Work hard and truly become...\N{\i1}the Hokage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto, good luck with\N{\i1}your never-say-die spirit...
Comment: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the regular report?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A fog is forming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the unit we're taking over for,\N it's apparently created by the Three-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It induces hallucinations, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's news to me, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You! That costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dam--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow! Deidara Senpai,\Nthat was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last of the lookouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your info was way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"A force separate from\Nthe Leaf Ninja was engaged
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in a vigorous clash over the Three-Tails."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it was supposed to be...\NThat's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But oh well, it's good that we got rid\Nof the ones in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make our quota right now\Nwhile we have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hundred years too young\Nto be giving me orders, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening about the hallucinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're speaking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate my art.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, he's got a short temper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a huge lake to find\Nthe Three-Tails in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be faster if it appeared on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! On closer inspection,\Nit looks something like a huge turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A powerful one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Three-Tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll leave it for you to handle,\NDeidara Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi, you formally became\Na member of Akatsuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the rest, hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a water creature,\Nshouldn't we have let Kisame handle it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say they assigned\Nthe wrong person for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitiful, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Comment: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The Pervy Sage disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he asked me\Nto give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of snacks\Nfor Gamatatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back to our village.\NPack up!
Comment: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! Banzai! Banzaai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Deidara, did you see my Jutsu?!\NJust one time, and bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can understand why\NI was given this important assignment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,right after formally becoming a member\Nof Akatsuki, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It was probably my clay bomb\Ndoing its artistic work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my artistry to thank, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so carried away that\Nyou forgot that I lent you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a member of Akatsuki,\Ndon't talk so much and act more cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, "cool = art"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, art is a passionate moment\Ncoming from cool emotions--!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, you talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was joking...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.05,0:24:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,contact from the unit that headed for\Nthe lake is rather late, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's file a report, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't press your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Three-Tails was just weak\Nbecause it didn't have a Jinchuriki host.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.60,0:24:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't have a mind to control its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.21,0:24:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so cool\Nas to stop talking altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.59,0:24:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At least answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.33,0:24:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that's the spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.43,0:24:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect wake up\Nfor you, I'd say. You bastard!
